Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:31.12,EDJ-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz270}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:34.97,EDJ-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz270}Sweet love in love world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:39.55,EDJ-2,,0,0,0,,{\frz270}You know what you wanna be
